## Shared SCSS (mixins · classes · tokens)

| Name | Path | Purpose | Reuse for |
|---|---|---|---|
| `mobile` / `tablet` / `tablet-up` / `desktop` / `wide` | `styles/_responsive.scss` | breakpoint mixins (mobile-first) | media queries |
| `fluid()` / `visually-hidden` / `respect-reduced-motion` | `styles/_mixins.scss` | fluid clamp() sizing + a11y helpers | responsive type, sr-only, motion |
| `--color-*` / `--space-*` / `--radius-*` / `--shadow-*` / `--ease-*` | `styles/_variables.scss` (`:root`) | design tokens (CSS custom properties) | all components |
| `--font-body` / `--font-mono` | `styles/_variables.scss` | font stacks | all typography |
| `[data-theme='dark']` overrides | `styles/_themes.scss` | runtime theme swap | theming |
